Class AdobePSDLayerComp

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.creativesdk.foundation.storage.AdobePSDLayerComp
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdobePSDMutableLayerComp

    public class AdobePSDLayerComp
extends java.lang.Object
    AdobePSDLayerComp presents the core interface to a composition of layers. It determines which layers are visible.
